pageContext.description: Ornamented round socket with 10 concentric parts of circles.  There are 10 of these figures (at B), each consists of 5 fine lines and an outside stronger line. 6 circles round rivet holes at A. In the centre is a punch mark. Damaged edges. A wooden shaft remains in good condition.
pageContext.associations: Hoard of leaf-shaped swords, spearheads, ferrules, and rings (53 articles in 63 fragments).
